org.apache.beam.runners.core

Class PushbackSideInputDoFnRunner<InputT,OutputT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.runners.core.PushbackSideInputDoFnRunner<InputT,OutputT>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DoFnRunner<InputT,OutputT>

    public class PushbackSideInputDoFnRunner<InputT,OutputT>
extends Object
implements DoFnRunner<InputT,OutputT>
    A DoFnRunner that can refuse to process elements that are not ready, instead returning them via the processElementInReadyWindows(WindowedValue).
